'''吉特曼氏綜合症'''（{{lang-en|Gitelman syndrome}}），又稱'''吉特曼症候群'''<ref name="kmu">{{cite journal | author =李雅婷、王一帆、林宗憲、黃洽鑽 | title =吉特曼症候群：三個病例報告與文獻回顧 | journal = | volume = | issue = | pages = |year=2006 | pmid = | doi = | url =http://ir.lib.kmu.edu.tw/bitstream/310902000/12710/1/PIIS1607551X09703237.pdf | issn = }}</ref>
，是一種常染色體隱性腎臟疾病，其特點是[[低鈣尿症|低鈣]]（hypocalciuria）、及[[低鎂血症|低鎂]]（hypomagnesemia）之[[低鉀血症|低鉀]][[代謝性鹼中毒|代謝性鹼中毒]]（Metabolic alkalosis）。它是由位在[[遠曲小管|遠曲小管]]（distal convoluted tubule）的[[噻嗪類|噻嗪類]]（thiazide）相關[[鈉氯同向轉運體|鈉氯同向轉運體]]（sodium-chloride symporter、亦稱為NCC、 NCCT、或TSC）的失活突變（inactivating mutation）所造成的功能喪失。<ref name="pmid8528245">{{cite journal | author = Simon DB, Nelson-Williams C, Bia MJ, Ellison D, Karet FE, Molina AM, Vaara I, Iwata F, Cushner HM, Koolen M, Gainza FJ, Gitleman HJ, Lifton RP | title = Gitelman's variant of Bartter's syndrome, inherited hypokalaemic alkalosis, is caused by mutations in the thiazide-sensitive Na-Cl cotransporter. | journal = Nat. Genet. | volume = 12 | issue = 1 | pages = 24–30 | date = Jan 1996 | pmid = 8528245 | doi = 10.1038/ng0196-24 | url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?term=david%20b%20simon%20gitelman's%20variant | issn =  | access-date = 2014-12-06 | archive-date = 2019-06-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190613152842/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?term=david%20b%20simon%20gitelman's%20variant | dead-url = no }}</ref>

吉特曼氏綜合症以前被認為包括在[[巴特氏症候群|巴特氏症候群]]裡，直到對這些疾病的不同的基因及分子基礎進行過鑑定。巴特氏症候群也是一種常染色體隱性低鉀代謝性鹼中毒，但它被發現在[[亨利氏環|亨利氏環]]（loop of Henle）[[亨利氏環升序肢體|升序肢體]]（Ascending limb of loop of Henle）裡從一個突變派生到[[鈉鉀氯共轉運蛋白|NKCC2]]。<ref name="pmid8640224">{{cite journal | author = Simon DB, Karet FE, Hamdan JM, DiPietro A, Sanjad SA, Lifton RP | title = Bartter's syndrome, hypokalaemic alkalosis with hypercalciuria, is caused by mutations in the Na-K-2Cl cotransporter NKCC2 | journal = Nat. Genet. | volume = 13 | issue = 2 | pages = 183–8 |date=June 1996 | pmid = 8640224 | doi = 10.1038/ng0696-183 | url = | issn = }}</ref>

