吉特曼氏綜合症鏈接到[[鈉氯同向轉運體|SLC12A3]]基因"失活的突變"造成編碼的敏感[[噻嗪類|噻嗪類]]（Thiazide）[[鈉氯同向轉運體|鈉氯同向轉運體]]（NCCT）的功能喪失。<!--This cell membrane protein participates in the control of ion [[homeostasis|homeostasis]] at the [[distal_convoluted_tubule|distal convoluted tubule]] portion of the [[nephron|nephron]].

Gitelman's syndrome is an [[autosome|autosomal]]-recessive disorder: one defective [[allele|allele]] has to be inherited from each parent.-->

==描述==
吉特曼氏綜合症病患所出現的症狀相同於服用[[噻嗪類|噻嗪類]][[利尿劑|利尿劑]]的病患所出現的症狀。<ref name="pmid15085183">{{cite journal |author=O'Shaughnessy KM, Karet FE |title=Salt handling and hypertension |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-clinical-investigation_2004-04_113_8/page/1075 |journal=J. Clin. Invest. |volume=113 |issue=8 |pages=1075–81 |year=2004 |pmid=15085183 |doi=10.1172/JCI200421560 |pmc=385413}}</ref>

本病的臨床症狀是[[低氯血症|低氯血性]]（hypochloremia）[[代謝性鹼中毒|代謝性鹼中毒]]（metabolic alkalosis）、[[低鉀血症|低鉀血症]]，及[[低鈣尿症|低鈣尿症]]（hypocalciuria）。<!--[[Hypomagnesemia|Hypomagnesemia]] is present in many but not all cases. In contrast to patients with [[Pseudohypoaldosteronism|Gordon's syndrome]], those suffering from Gitelman's syndrome are generally normotensive. Carriers of Gitelman's syndrome-linked mutations are often asymptomatic while some complain of mild muscular [[cramp|cramp]]s or weakness expressed as fatigue or irritability. More severe symptoms such as [[tetany_(medical_sign)|tetany]] and [[paralysis|paralysis]] have however also been reported. Phenotypic variations observed among patients probably result from differences in their genetic background and may depend on which particular amino acid in the NCCT protein has been mutated.

See Naesens ''et al.'' for a recent review.<ref name="pmid15056980">{{cite journal |author=Naesens M, Steels P, Verberckmoes R, Vanrenterghem Y, Kuypers D |title=Bartter's and Gitelman's syndromes: from gene to clinic |journal=Nephron. Physiology |volume=96 |issue=3 |pages=p65–78 |year=2004 |pmid=15056980 |doi=10.1159/000076752}}</ref>-->

==命名==
它以一位美國醫生[[希勒爾·J.·吉特曼|希勒爾·J.·吉特曼]]（Hillel J. Gitelman、1932-2015）而命名。<ref>{{WhoNamedIt|synd|2329}}</ref><ref name="pmid5929460">{{cite journal |author=Gitelman HJ, Graham JB, Welt LG |title=A new familial disorder characterized by hypokalemia and hypomagnesemia |journal=Trans. Assoc. Am. Physicians |volume=79 |issue= |pages=221–35 |year=1966 |pmid=5929460 |doi=}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author=Unwin RJ, Capasso G | title=Bartter's and Gitelman's syndromes: their relationship to the actions of loop and thiazide diuretics | journal=CURRENT OPINION IN PHARMACOLOGY | volume=6 | issue=2 | year=2006 | pages=208–213 | url=http://147.83.15.91/Doc/cols_new/contenidos/data/072854502093.3.Sindromes_Gitelman_Barter.pdf | format=[[PDF|PDF]] | id= | pmid=16490401 | doi=10.1016/j.coph.2006.01.002 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023060532/http://147.83.15.91/Doc/cols_new/contenidos/data/072854502093.3.Sindromes_Gitelman_Barter.pdf | archivedate=2013-10-23 | access-date=2014-12-06 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://paw.princeton.edu/memorial/hillel-j-gitelman-%E2%80%9954 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2017-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170326230329/https://paw.princeton.edu/memorial/hillel-j-gitelman-%E2%80%9954 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

